{"data":[{"id":563785837,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"71aa14386245f454bf88b247f4ab4d4b","url_token":"yu-jiang-76-50","name":"曦尔薇","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d9add1da92df182293b119e58508165d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d9add1da92df182293b119e58508165d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/71aa14386245f454bf88b247f4ab4d4b","user_type":"people","headline":"来成为小恶魔，和堕天使夜羽一起堕天吧","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1149,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563785837","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8b65559422050269b72809b42e4de378_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546276837,"updated_time":1546278771,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":93,"comment_count":12,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"disallowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀，首先不得不佩服他的“人气”，文章发出34分钟，获得2200赞同，5000+评论……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且，我收到了无数的邀请。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d54be178ec24f747ce2c01b4f685dfb_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c757ee88c9d87c277de075514a0f2c27_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d54be178ec24f747ce2c01b4f685dfb_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='2436'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c757ee88c9d87c277de075514a0f2c27_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d54be178ec24f747ce2c01b4f685dfb_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d54be178ec24f747ce2c01b4f685dfb_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d5716f99886bcf1b5ff3d865d772cbb_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04bfbef3e0336e4624cdf623c443eed7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d5716f99886bcf1b5ff3d865d772cbb_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='2436'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04bfbef3e0336e4624cdf623c443eed7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d5716f99886bcf1b5ff3d865d772cbb_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d5716f99886bcf1b5ff3d865d772cbb_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e先来看看他的准备工作吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e准备:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e1.设集合 A 为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数。\u003cbr\u003e2.设集合 B 为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数只包括正质数。\u003cbr\u003e3.任意大于等于4的偶数均可以表示为 6k-2 ， 6k ， 6k+2 中的一种。其中k为正整数。\u003cbr\u003e目的:证明任意n∈ N^* 且n \\geq 2时，2n∈B是真命题。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e“有借有还再借不难”法……证明老哥真的开拓数学领域，有借有还、再借不难了（）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过……负质数？我从来都没听过“质数”还有负的啊……姑且认为是质数的相反数吧……往下看。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a1cfaca016e56e1fabc98e71b7357021_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4b52cce3fb5e1ef51b9d1512085f4679_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a1cfaca016e56e1fabc98e71b7357021_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4b52cce3fb5e1ef51b9d1512085f4679_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a1cfaca016e56e1fabc98e71b7357021_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a1cfaca016e56e1fabc98e71b7357021_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫猜想变式1……这不是废话吗…… 2n=(-1)+(2n-1) ，然后……2n属于A，就这几步……谁告诉你质数是 2n+1 的……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后我又看了后面的几个推导…… -1 改成了 -3 ， -5 ……证明过程大体一样，证明老哥刚好验证了：\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e人类的本质是复读机！\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-45406eed1e298948bc60b6fc56d7595b_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fea452ca428f9a8dc2bc8b336166a509_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-45406eed1e298948bc60b6fc56d7595b_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='960'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fea452ca428f9a8dc2bc8b336166a509_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-45406eed1e298948bc60b6fc56d7595b_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-45406eed1e298948bc60b6fc56d7595b_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7a31f43085cc2c093518007e7b7d67e7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2e8e4bee5e6c8477cd5ed5c1334097a3_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7a31f43085cc2c093518007e7b7d67e7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='960'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2e8e4bee5e6c8477cd5ed5c1334097a3_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7a31f43085cc2c093518007e7b7d67e7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7a31f43085cc2c093518007e7b7d67e7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-27d43192475a413a969db17a784894cc_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3cb2561df0ff8b18c31a7bfbf34a86c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-27d43192475a413a969db17a784894cc_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3cb2561df0ff8b18c31a7bfbf34a86c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-27d43192475a413a969db17a784894cc_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-27d43192475a413a969db17a784894cc_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这证明就看到这里了，我已经不想再看了……错误百出……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明老哥的有借有还再借不难法……本质是“把一个假命题设为真，然后证明一个命题为真”，一个高中生稍微想想就知道这是有问题并且在数学里是不合理的好趴！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e不用想，看了他的证明可以知道两点。\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e1. 他连高考的难题都不会做，这种过程可以说是经典无效骗分法；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2. 他进入数学系，八成会学不下去转专业或是退学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本来以为他能说点什么新奇的东西，结果看完这个证明的过程，我觉得他可能连高考里的难题都做不出来……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些人其实经常眼高手低、好高骛远，再加上哗众取宠，就造成了今天这种事情的出现……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e唉……希望这位题主经历了这件事情以后能够踏踏实实学习吧……当然我还是祝他高考加油。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53752361\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b9bd761a671c557f6ee865f4e35c40ba_r.jpg\" data-image-width=\"690\" data-image-height=\"502\" class=\"internal\"\u003e曦尔薇：拜读了“证明”老哥的哥德巴赫猜想证明\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1:50，知乎已经看不下去把他的文章之类的都清零了，此人肉眼掉粉中（）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-913482a9b940a14bf62849f2a81e3877_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4de5a4c341f24a5df227b2c54e40a1cb_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-913482a9b940a14bf62849f2a81e3877_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;s